page.title: 14HEALTH PAGE 1
page.content:
My is name Keith and my mum is on a diet, but instead of losing weight she puts it on.
I am fair healthy but I am a little colour blind.I go to the health clinic once a year to have my eyes tested.My Doctor is doctor G.H. Cooper but I know some other doctors called Dr.Brown and Dr.Chapman.
A year ago I was playing tennis and as I struck, the bat hit my front tooth and it broke in half.Next day I went to the dentist and they put a cap on.I went back to school but it came off while I was playing out,so I had to go to dentist again.They put a stronger cap on.Now I go for a check on my teeth at least every two months.
